Subject: [warriors_eq] Demon Claw


>From: "Jason Coan" <COANJ@...>
>
>Damn I feel cool now, scored me a Demon Claw this weekend. What is a Demon
Claw, well its a really nice, really cool looking, magic 1h slashing weapon
that the Avitar of Fear carries. The AoF is high, real high, 30s, 38 or so,
but his claw kicks butt. Damage is only 5, but speed is 19, yes 19, I swing
it about 6 or 8 times in the time it takes me to swing my BBC just twice.
In some fights I swear the thing swings almost continusouly. Needless to
say, this weapon has restored my faith in dual wielding.
